itunes:summary:
Ross Patterson goes backstage with Asking Alexandria lead singer/Drinkin' Bros Theme song creator Danny Worsnop live from Akron, Ohio to discuss his new solo album that is racing up the Itunes charts, why he only pees sitting down, and what point you are drunk enough to stab an alligator in the head with a kitchen knife.  Things get out of hand after the 10th shot in the 2nd half of the show.
